Richard Montanari - Four Novels of Suspense Book Bundle 

(Kevin Byrne and Jessica Balzano series) - Retail (epub)


1. The Rosary Girls; 

2. The Skin Gods; 

3. Merciless; 

4. Badlands

In internationally bestselling author Richard Montanari's acclaimed suspense series, veteran homicide cops Kevin Byrne and Jessica Balzano crack some of the most shocking and terrifying cases ever to hit Philadelphia. From a killer who re-creates Hollywood death scenes to a madman who uses the City of Brotherly Love as his gruesome game board, Byrne and Balzano have seen it all in their relentless pursuit of justice. 

This convenient eBook bundle takes you back to the beginning with four chilling novels: The Rosary Girls, The Skin Gods, Merciless, and Badlands.
